own.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0cd82eb5f16410e75eaf69e472cf1d0bb0566de","tid":1896623,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T09:00:41.000Z","msg":"成個站嘅空氣系統<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢排經過旺角東站都有機已奶野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"172dc1682f493bf86dc32b61138c33669a13fbb6","tid":1896623,"uid":303805,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T09:00:52.000Z","msg":"黨鐵前線好白"},{"pid":"f52841b4327072b7c9cc6540586dd276b9d66fe4","tid":1896623,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T09:02:53.000Z","msg":"本港新增3宗新型肺炎確診個案，包括旺角東站一名站務主任。港鐵說，已根據當局指引，用1:49 漂白水深層次徹底清潔和消毒，確保車站環境衞生。另外，已加強全綫車站及列車的清潔和消毒工作，為車站員工提供口罩，員工執勤時須戴上口罩，亦為有需要員工提供眼罩及手套。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵說，該名站務主任上星期五休息，星期六起放病假，他的家人星期日確診患病，他在同日起接受強制檢疫，昨日在家中自行量體溫時發現輕微發燒，被送到聯合醫院診治。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示，星期日得知站務主任家人被確診後，已要求曾與站務主任有密切接觸的員工，分別留在家中自我隔離及聯絡衞生署，亦安排醫學專家向旺角東站人員講解，並提供所需支援。"},{"pid":"b2fa60b6539ced714dcfd27c513934e9df52c242","tid":1896623,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T09:11:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=9db65a4b\" data-auto-link targe